<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-16 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-16">
    <div class="text-lg">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Purpose</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500"><span class="text-black font-bold">The University of Oxford Romanian Society (OxRoSoc) exists to foster a close-knit community of Romanian students and those interested in Romanian culture.</span> We aim to celebrate and promote Romania's rich traditions, while providing social, cultural, and academic support to our members through a variety of events, activities, and networking opportunities. Our society is a space for building meaningful connections and sharing the unique Romanian heritage within the diverse Oxford environment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-lg">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">What we've done so far</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500"><span class="text-black font-bold">OxRoSoc has proudly organized a wide range of events that bring together the Romanian community at Oxford.</span> From celebrating traditional Romanian holidays like Mărțișor and Dragobete to hosting formal dinners, pub socials, and cultural movie nights, we've created spaces for both relaxation and cultural exchange.</p>
